{"tid":1570534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盾唔需要被矛保護","createTime":"2019-09-15T06:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:44:32.000Z","uid":291996,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3fc6631c384150e5acb6c7c43657f68bf558eb","tid":1570534,"uid":291996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:22:40.000Z","msg":"成日見人話勇武因為要保護和理非而被拉。<br />\n<br />\n唔係想否定勇武，但和理非係盾，根本唔需要被矛（勇武）保護。<br />\n<br />\n和理非要走自然就會走（唔少走得快過你添&hellip;），勇武真係不必要有假設話要保護和理非而唔走。<br />\n<br />\n其實如果勇武走中前排就自動會走&hellip; 和理非其實相對安全&hellip; 一齊安全返屋企好過啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f07ada417c6ab89c8bad10513027ad57ae0bc03","tid":1570534,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:24:35.000Z","msg":"[929]全球遊行進度，致世界信，幫手廣傳，比各外國手足見到 (English post)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3d32efceab8c0a6f0b53dffc8b4c089cf4be01f","tid":1570534,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推 勇武退我地自然退<br />\n不被捕 不受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9270a502807ced01ff9395cdc71306411e915dd2","tid":1570534,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁<br />\n[重要] 見到藍絲要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ada4bde2bacd1f0de6f067dda361f08fa7fadb21","tid":1570534,"uid":175346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20bae5afab7026590527c303ec2cc2c743fdbc24","tid":1570534,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"