":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:37:22.000Z","msg":"一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3e8d2a305570804b7232aa88a4c1fc86e5708a","tid":1570534,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"而家係話中後排頂撚住走唔到呀<br />\n無心理準備就唔好企到咁撚前 一開波又閃唔切頂住前面啲手足"},{"pid":"deb80d0136be93e5067d6248ad15031583e8d3a3","tid":1570534,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"和理非冇太多野係手，點都好過勇武俾狗斷正ge"},{"pid":"2947cbabec33fa70044e41d088bbf15e5528c13a","tid":1570534,"uid":287829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"同意，其實我一直有呢個想法，只係唔敢講，怕話我係分化撚。<br />\n<br />\n勇武巴打做完road block或覺得要走一定要走先，少一個就少一個。和理非被拉，gear少啲，未必咁易告入嚴重罪行，最多非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n每一個人出嚟都有自己法律責任，唔可以要勇武巴食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2b56514041b22f01aa38879812af3488635bca","tid":1570534,"uid":322550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"勇武走先！和理行街！"}]}